Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Disables Diagnostic Hub Standard Collector Service.
; Collects performance and diagnostic data for Microsoft.
; Only useful for developers using Visual Studio diagnostics tools.
; WARNING: Skip if you use Visual Studio performance profiling tools.

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\diagnosticshub.standardcollector.service]
"Start"=dword:00000004
